
This package is designed for use with the latest version of Wolfpack.
Wolfpack Homepage: http://www.wpdev.org/

Place this entire package in: /path/to/wolfpack_shard/

You should then have: /path/to/wolfpack_shard/rayonnant/

Then open /path/to/wolfpack_shard/wolfpack.xml and change the following

For definitions change:
	<!-- Old -->
	<option key="Definitions" value="definitions/index.xml" />
	<!-- New -->
	<option key="Definitions" value="definitions/index.xml;rayonnant/definitions/index.xml" />

For scripts change:
	<!-- Old -->
	<option key="Python Searchpath" value="./scripts;." />
	<!-- New -->
	<option key="Python Searchpath" value="./scripts;./rayonnant;." />

After this you may want to change the starting locations:

	<group name="StartLocation" >
		<option key="Location 1" value="Yew=1508,1687,10,0" />
		<option key="Location 2" value="Minoc=1508,1687,10,0" />
		<option key="Location 3" value="Britain=1508,1687,10,0" />
		<option key="Location 4" value="Moonglow=1508,1687,10,0" />
		<option key="Location 5" value="Trinsic=1508,1687,10,0" />
		<option key="Location 6" value="Magincia=1508,1687,10,0" />
		<option key="Location 7" value="Jhelom=1508,1687,10,0" />
		<option key="Location 8" value="Skara Brae=1508,1687,10,0" />
		<option key="Location 9" value="Vesper=1508,1687,10,0" />
	</group>

Using that should have your players always start in Thalos.

Thank you and enjoy!

